claim.claim-text:
A transition duct (26) comprising;

a frame (50) at an aft end (48) of the transition duct (26), the frame (50) having a downstream end (54), a radially outer portion (60), a radially inner portion (58) opposed to the radially outer portion (60), a first side portion (62) between the radially outer and inner portions (60,58), and a second side portion (64) opposed to the first side portion (62) between the radially outer and inner portions (60,58);

a slot (66) in the first side portion (62) of the frame (50), the slot (66) having a downstream surface (70) adjacent to the downstream end (54) of the frame (50); and

a heat shield (72) having an inner surface (74), an outer surface (76) and a plurality of spacers (78) that extend outward from the inner surface (74), wherein the inner surface (74) is adjacent to the slot (66) downstream surface (70) and the frame downstream end (54).
